<br>
So my question is are there any Wizard only, or mostly wizard guilds out there?  If so, what are their names, and what servers are they on?<br>
<br>
Also, it's been my experience that these types of guilds never really take off.  Why is that, considering that I hear so often on class boards of strange groups consisting of mostly one class being really awesome?  The last class only guild I can remember was the &quot;Sanguine Blade&quot; or some such, for rogues..  But I think it died out some time back, not sure though.<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=nadiar>Nadiar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Arcanist<BR>Mistyr Smartipants</span><br>  Posts: 1232<br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/29/03 7:47 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Wizard only guilds?</span><hr size=1> There is an all bard guild on Firiona Vie. I can't remember the name, its something liek Molto Espresso.  You can read about it more on eqDiva.<br>
<br>
And haven't you been paying attention? Wizards suck, we can't group worth shit, we don't do dps, we add nothing to groups so we have to solo, and we can't even port whore anymore, omg! <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=8991"><br>
<!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.nadiar.com/bcsig.gif" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=dalrenfieryblade>Dalren Fieryblade</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Channeler</span><br>  Posts: 205<br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/29/03 7:51 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Wizard only guilds?</span><hr size=1>  Bah I hope you where being sarcastic, because you are wrong <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  Wizards do awsome damage if they take the time to get their nukes. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=490410">Dalren Fieryblade of Tarew Marr</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=claudshadowflare>ClaudShadowflare</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Arcanist<BR>Has Eddie Murphy's<BR>taste in women</span><br>  Posts: 3638<br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/29/03 7:59 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Wizard only guilds?</span><hr size=1> ...I was wondering if he was being sarcastic myself, but then I looked at the edges of my monitor and noticed that my screen was practically dripping with sarcasm... <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=izenblazeincindevesor>Izenblaze Incindevesor</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Arcanist<br>Don't 