Leage of non aligned wizards <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=harvestofsouls>Harvest of Souls</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Evoker</span><br>  Posts: 282<br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/29/03 10:47 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ...</span><hr size=1> we had one called pheonix wizardry on druzzil that i was an officer in way back when.. the plan being to corner the port market and set up a standard rate for the server.. /sigh.. was a happy thought but only lasted a few months hehe<br>
<br>
inc <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=ziggie204>ziggie204</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br>  Posts: 53<br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/29/03 11:41 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ...</span><hr size=1> I dont know, it could be possible.  Lets say a guild fields 40 people for a raid on a mob.  If you could line up 40 60+ wizards, and they cast at the same time, that could add up to some serious damage.  Not to mention, they could then continue to cast again while some wizards get summoned and eaten.  If the mob can only summon every 5 seconds, they could get off a couple casts at least before all were dead.   They could take down some interesting encounters.  Of course they would have to bot some to get to these encounters and will need a cleric to rez their dead butts.<br>
<br>
It really would be a kick to see it happen.<br>
<br>
They could down Vindi and Velks in one shot.  Once the hps of the mob got about 200k there might be some more serious flaws. <p><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.bound-by-honor.com/images/upload/members/ziggiesig2.jpg" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=artillis>Artillis</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Arcanist<BR>Enjoys Sheep Erotica</span><br>  Posts: 1887<br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/30/03 12:05 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ...</span><hr size=1> I was seriously considering starting an all wizard guild on the FV server back when I played on it, but couldn't find enuff wizards willing to do it.  I found some good wizards that I probably could of used to help get it started but for something like that I was looking for certain specific character traits to help for a strong foundation to build upon and get it started and didn't find what I wanted.  Without the right people to form a solid foundation of wizards that are willing to roleplay and have fun with a all wizard guild on the FV server, I knew it would fall apart quickly. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=nadiar>Nadiar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Arcanist<BR>Mistyr Smartipants</span><br>  Posts: 1234<br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/30/03 12:39 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ...</span><hr size=1> The entire concept makes no sense at all to me.<br>
<br>
If you want to make a clan of wizards, start a website, start a channel.  Let them do whatever you want with their own guild, just come up with a loose set of guidelines for what you want to accomplish.  Thats essentially what most 'Team Manaburn's were.  Sure, many were guilded with the other wizards, but the most important binding facet was that they were all friends.  Just find a bunch of people who want to be able to do things with only wizards, and you're set.  The lack of a guild tag doesn't mean you can't associate with them. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=zertez>zertez</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br>  Posts: 145<br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/30/03 1:02 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ...</span><hr size=1>  On BB there was an all Druid RP guild a few years ago, Silent Thunder. They did pretty good and were around for awhile, not as long as SB, the all rogue guild but both made it over a year.<br>
<br>
 They could not do some of the harder things in game but they did pretty well overall. Most of the all 'insert any class' guilds are gone now, most were RP guilds, guess they died with most of the RP in EQ. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showPrevMessage?topicID=26729.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showNextMessage?topicID=26729.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.emailToFriend?topicID=26729.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.threadControl?topicID=26729.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=26729.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=26729.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to stop receiving email notification of replies"> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies</a> <br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub140.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>j